## The kind of work I take on next

Most active enquiries are for:

- Small business [WordPress builds](/website-design/wordpress/) at Starter or Standard package size
- [Redesigns](/website-design/redesign/) of existing UK service business websites where the leads have plateaued
- B2B service / consultancy sites at Growth package size

Less common but welcome:

- Healthcare clinics (private and dental)
- Law firms and legal practices
- WooCommerce builds for service businesses adding products

What I don't take on:

- Pure ecommerce above 100 SKUs (Shopify specialists are better)
- Magento builds solo (partner-only)
- Sites where the brief is "just make it look modern" without a measurable goal

